B.Uz=s([B.Kf,B.Kx,B.L_],t.l)
B.R1=new A.T(B.ad,"Advanced Clearance Examples",null,B.Uz,null,null)
B.QQ=new A.T(B.ae,"\u2708\ufe0f Advanced Exam Tips",'Conditional clearances \u2014 always identify:\n1. **Condition** \u2014 which aircraft / when\n2. **Instruction** \u2014 what to do\n3. **Readback** must include the condition: "Behind the B777 on final, cleared to land, THY456"\n\nOceanic clearances always include: track letter + FL + Mach number + squawk\n\nEFC (Expect Further Clearance) is NOT a clearance to leave the hold \u2014 the pilot must wait for the actual clearance.',null,null,null)
